Elotunoto e Nkiyang'et Sinyati


1   Ore pee ebau enkolong o Pentekoste, netii apa pooki ewueji nebo. 
2  Ore nabo kata nelotu enkikurrukur naing'uaa keper neeijo eno lkutati, neiput ina aji pooki natii ninche. 
3  Nedol ninche entoki neeijo lng'ejepa le nkima eisuaari: neiseyie ake ina ng'ejep neeijo enkima o lng'ejep le pooki tung'ani otii ine. 
4  Neigany Enkiyang'et Sinyati ninche pooki neiteru aairo kulie kutukie, anaa enaidimie Enkiyang'et Sinyati meiroro.


5  Nemanya Yerusalem Ilyahudi laa iltung'ana asayiak le Nkai, ooetuo ninche eing'uaa nkuapi pooki e nkop. 
6  Ore pee ening ina kikurrukur neiturrurro olorora kitok. Neiputukuny neing'asia pooki amu meetae ake oleitu ening ninche eiro enkutuk naikini ninye. 
7  Neiputukuny neing'asia nejo, “Amaa kulo tung'ana aime Lgalilaya pooki! 
8  Aainyo naa pee kining'ito iyiook pooki eiro nkutukie ang naaikini iyiook? 
9  King'uaa iyiook Partia, Media, Elam; niking'uaa Mesopotamia, Yudea, o Kapodokia; niking'uaa Ponto o Asia, 
10  niking'uaa Frigia o Pamfiliam niking'uaa Misiri o lkirinen le Libya o Kirene, neing'uaa kulikae lang Roma, 
11  ndung'ot pokira, Lyahudi o Loreren ooibelekenyate aaku Lyahudi; niking'uaa kulikae lang Krete o Arabia kake eji nikining pooki eiro ninche nkutukie ang eimaki mbaa kituaak naataasa Enkai!” 
12  Ore eing'asiate pooki nemilo neikilikuana taa ake aajo, “Ainyoo eutu ena bae?”


13  Kake etii ilookueniyie ilairukok ejo, “Ketemerate kulo tung'ana!”

Ilomon ooinosua Petero


14  Kake neinyototo Petero eboitare ninye lelo kulikae tomon o obo, neiteru airorie olorere to ltoilo sapuk ajoki, “Lo lewa lang loo Lyahudi, o intae pooki oomanya Yerusalem, entoning enajo, matoliki intae enautu ena bae. 
15  Eitu emera kulo tung'ana anaa ina nijojo, ene uni ena saa anaa pee ekenyu. 
16  Maa, enapa bae ena natolimuo oloiboni le Nkai oji Yoel pee ejo,


17   ‘Kaas ena bae te nena olong'i naabayie, Enkai najo,

kabukoki ltung'ana pooki Enkiyang'et ai.

Keyooki aaibonisho layiok linyi o ntoyie inyi;

nedol ilbarnot linyi nduaat, netum ilpayiani linyi nkidetidetat.


18  Ee, o metabaiki sii ninche sinkan laainei, loo lewa o loo ng'oruo,

kabukoki Enkiyang'et ai te nena olong'i, naa keibonisho kenya ninche.


19  Naa kaitodolu ine nking'asia te ntaiya e shumata,

o sapiipiyieti ti abori te nkop.

Nedoli osarge o enkima, o empuruo nairrusha:


20  neitomisimisi enkolong, nedoru olapa atiu anaa osarge,

eton etiooyo ina olong o Laitoriani, enkolong kitok e nkisisa.


21  Ore te ina kata, ore pooki ng'ae oipot

enkarna o Laitoriani neitajeuni.’


22  “Lo lewa le Israeli! Entoning kulo rorei. Ore Yesu le Nasaretii, oltung'ani otisirua Enkai abaraki te intae too mbaa e ngolon o ine nking'asia o nkitoduaat o lmonek ooitaasa intae Enkai te nkaina enye; niyiololo intae ina amu atua intae etaasieki. 
23   Enkai openy natudutayie te yieunoto o te ng'eno enye makewan apake nchere, keitarasari Yesu, nitara intae ninye, aaisho ltung'ana arruok metasho. 
24   Kake eitopiwuo Enkai ninye aitung'uaa ilootuata: nelaku aoru emion e keeya amu meidimayu apa neenikino enkeeya ninye. 
25   Amu eimaka Daudi ninye nejo,

‘Atoduaa Olaitoriani etii dukuya nanu nkatitin pooki:

aatii te tatene, metaa maaigusugusieki.


26  Amu ore te nkaraki ena keng'ida oltau lai,

nebore irorei laainei enchipai; ore nanu, nara ake olenye,

nayeng'iyeng'a aanyisho to siligi,


27  amu ming'uaa iyie oltau lai te nemeneng'a,

nimincho osinka lino sinyati metupurdayu ang'uoyu.


28  Kituutaka iyie nanu inkoitoi enkishui,

ore amu itii iyie, ei kilo aiput enchipai.’


29  “Ilalashera laainei, enchooki maibalakinye intae ashirraki too mbaa e papa lang Daudi, Etua ninye, nenukari, netii enkurare enye atua iyiook o tene. 
30   O loiboni le Nkai apa metaa ketayiolo ina naisiligie Enkai ajoki, ore eishoi enye keikini likae aiguanani kitok oitoreisho anaa apa Daudi. 
31  Ina etodolua Daudi naas kenya ake Enkai, paa keiroro aimaki empiunoto e Kristo pee ejo: ‘Eitu eing'uari ninye te nemeneng'a. Neitu epurda osesen lenye ang'uoyu.’


32  “Ele Yesu likiimaki eitopiwuo Enkai aitung'uaa ilootuata, nikira iyiook lchakenini le ina bae. 
33  Ore pee eilepieki nepiki tatene e Nkai, neng'amu Enkiyang'et Sinyati te Menye anaa enatejo apake; naa ore ena nidolitata nining'itoto ina kishorunoto enye etubukoko iyiook. 
34   Amu eitu elo Daudi makewan keper; kake etejo ninye kewan, ‘Etiaka Olaitoriani Olaitoriani lai: Totona te tatene ai, 
35  pee aitadou ilmang'ati linono metotiutu anaa olorika loo nkejek inono.’ 
36  Entayioloito naa taata enkaji pooki e Israel ena nadede nchere, ele Yesu, lishomo intae aashe to salaba, eitaa Enkai Olaitoriani o Kristo.”


37  Kuna ake etoning'o ninche nerem ilo rorei iltauja, nejoki Petero o lkulikae kipaareta, “Kaa naa kiaas, ilalashera lang?”


38  Nejoki Petero ninche, “Erridutu pooki tung'ani, neibatisai pooki te intae te nkarna e Yesu Kristo, pee epalakini intae ng'ok inyi; naa ing'amumu enkishorunoto e Enkiyang'et Sinyati. 
39  Amu ore ena kisiligata eninyi apa o nkera inyi, o lelo pooki oolakua lelo pooki ooipotoki Enkai kewan.”


40  Neitirrishaki Petero aitadedeyie te kulie baa kumok, nejoki, “Entajeu ate te ina nainepu kulo tung'ana arruok.” 
41  Neiruk ilkumok nena baa naainosua ninye, neibatisai; neponikini ilo turrur iltung'ana oobaya nkalifuni uni te ina olong. 
42  Neaku ketumo ninche anaa ake te nkiteng'enare oo lkipaareta, neshulare aaisiritore, neng'arie endaa, neshulare te nkomono.

Enataasa lelo ooiruko Yesu


43  Nejing aiput enkuretisho pooki ng'ae; neasi inenking'asia, olmonek too lkipaareta. 
44   Nebik ilairukok pooki te nebo te nchula neyau masaa enye aang'ar. 
45  Neaku kemir masaa enye o ntokitin naata neorikino pooki mpesai, anaa enaatayie oltung'ani enkolat. 
46  Netumo anaa ake ilo turrur te nkaji e Nkai, neng'ar ndaiki too nkajijik enye, neng'ida edaa to ltau obo, 
47  neisis Enkai, neshipakino iltung'ana pooki ninche. Neponaa Olaitoriani ilo turrur lenye anaa ake te lelo ooitajeuni.

